item.title: CVE-2024-34689|2024-07-09T04:18:21.258Z -- sap_se -- sap%20business%20workflow%20%28webflow%20services%29
item.description: WebFlow Services of SAP Business Workflow allows an authenticated attacker to enumerate accessible HTTP endpoints in the internal network by specially crafting HTTP requests. On successful exploitation this can result in information disclosure. It has no impact on integrity and availability of the application.
